<h2>Thank You for Your Rental Request!</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @rental_request.name %>,</p>

<p>We've received your request for an Ocean City vacation rental. Our concierge team is already working on finding the perfect property for you!</p>

<h3>What You're Looking For:</h3>
<ul>
  <% if @rental_request.bedrooms.present? %><li><strong>Bedrooms:</strong> <%= @rental_request.bedrooms %></li><% end %>
  <% if @rental_request.bathrooms.present? %><li><strong>Bathrooms:</strong> <%= @rental_request.bathrooms %></li><% end %>
  <% if @rental_request.sleeps.present? %><li><strong>Sleeps:</strong> <%= @rental_request.sleeps %> guests</li><% end %>
  <% if @rental_request.check_in_date.present? %><li><strong>Check-in:</strong> <%= @rental_request.check_in_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li><% end %>
  <% if @rental_request.check_out_date.present? %><li><strong>Check-out:</strong> <%= @rental_request.check_out_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li><% end %>
</ul>

<h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Our local Ocean City experts will review your request</li>
  <li>We'll search our database for properties matching your criteria</li>
  <li>You'll receive personalized recommendations within 24 hours</li>
</ol>

<p>If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reply to this email or call us.</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  <strong>The OCNJ Weekly Rentals Team</strong><br>
  <a href="https://ocnjweeklyrentals.com">ocnjweeklyrentals.com</a>
</p>
